description: For sale: $195,000. Unbelievable space with this 4 bedroom 2 bath sprawling rambler. Spring will be here for you to enjoy the paver patio and beautifully landscaped yard on almost 1 2 acre! Enjoy the small town charm as you stroll around town or head to the local restaurant. Storage shed in rear property stays as well as carport frame.  Waterville, Elysian, Morristown bus comes to Warsaw.

For sale: $120,000. Affordable and better than rent! Why pay rent to someone else when you can own your own home! One level living on a nice one half acre lot. Room to park your RV with electrical hookup. Enjoy a bonfire on your own private paver patio in the back yard or relax on your enclosed front porch and enjoy the water view. Newer roof, maintenance free siding and flooring. Spacious kitchen and a surprising amount of storage room. Plenty of room to build your man cave/she shed on the property. This is a unique opportunity to own your own home with a view of Cannon Lake. Easy walk to go fishing. Enjoy recreational activities just minutes from Sakatah Singing Hills State Trail.

description: Recently sold: $192,900. Hard to find! Adorable and nicely kept home.  Country feel, close to Cannon Lake.  Home is bigger than it looks from the outside!  Sitting proudly on 1.25 Acres of mature trees and stunning landscaping that includes: firepit with serving station/bar, concrete patio and Pergola.  Perfect for entertaining.  This home features: 3 Bedrooms, 1 bath, office and loft. Many updates and improvements seen thru out the home.  Gleaming floors, open floor plan, comfortable living.  Main floor bedroom.  Lovely kitchen.  Furnace is approximately 1 year old.  New well tank in April 2019.  Septic shall be in compliance.  Own for less than rent.
